messages.message: hey team, when will the feature ‘check in all file’ in aihub be available?
Do you mean conversation with multiple files?

i just run a POV, where we got an email with attachments as an input. we built the solution with LLM.
We extracted all fields per attachment, but the requirement was: extract the fields from all documents at once.
Thats why i am asking

Yeah, lot of users have asked for it. We are first focused on making large docs processing better where information needs to be collated from multiple chunks. This same capability will help us unlock the multiple files later. We will share an ETA later this quarter, as we finish scoping Q3 roadmap.
